These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
City: colone, nizza, prague, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| City        | colone | nizza   | san-francisco | prague    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, august, april, march
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in january is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Birthday   | march    | january | april | august    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, sailing, tennis, ice-hockey
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | ice-hockey | tennis | sailing    | volleyball      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, cola, coffee
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking coffee##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Beverage   | cola       | sprite   | iced-tea    | coffee  |

