.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, rowing, surfing, badminton
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the indian is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Sport   | rowing  | handball    | surfing   | badminton       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

