.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
House: wooden, cottage, gothic-revival, futuristic
1. the cottage house is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the cottage house##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the wooden house is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| House   | futuristic | cottage     | wooden  | gothic-revival  |

