.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, mystery, western
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, june, january, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Birthday     | december | january  | february     | june |

