.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, manager, writer, nurse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. the police-officer is the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the police-officer##1
3. the fan of jazz is between the fan of disco and the writer##2
4. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the manager is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Job      | manager       | writer   | police-officer | nurse |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

