.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, reggae, d&b, ambient
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, ambient-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the fan of disco##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is ambient-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is ambient-polo is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | ambient   | reggae      | d&b      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | ambient-polo | biathlon |

