.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, carrot, cherry, lemon
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, march, september, april
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
3. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
4. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cherry is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in september##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | lemon | carrot  | cherry  | cabbage |
| Birthday   | april  | september | october | march   |

