The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, aconite, marigold, azalea
1. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
4. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person who growsaconite is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | drama | satire | thriller  |
| Flower     | aconite   | tulip  | azalea  | marigold |

