2. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the manager##1
4. the nurse is on the right of the mechanic##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the nurse is on the left or right of the mechanic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | western | family | martial-arts |
| Job           | mechanic     | nurse     | manager   | bartender         |

