.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, american, turkish, french
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the turkish##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the russian##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the french##1
4. the turkish is on the left or right of the french##3
5. the russian is in an even position##4
6. the turkish is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality   | american | russian | turkish    | french |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

