.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, time-travel, crime, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, nigerian, turkish
1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
3. the japanese is the person watching crime movies##1
4. the nigerian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the japanese is between the turkish and the nigerian##2
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | animation   | crime | spy | time-travel    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese  | turkish     | american |

