.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, tiparillo, dunhill, alhambra
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the tiparillo-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person driving the helicopter##2
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | dunhill   | alhambra | tiparillo |
| Transport   | van          | jet-ski | helicopter         | subway  |

 